Introduction

Kai Kamal Huening is a Brazilian/American-South Korean singer-songwriter and composer under BIGHIT MUSIC and HYBE Labels. He is the first foreign artist in the company. He is best known as the maknae of the boy group TXT. Beyond his vocal talents, Hueningkai has also contributed significantly to TXT’s music production, having worked on eight of their songs under the producer name Producer Hue.

On January 15, 2019, Kai was revealed as the third member of TXT. The group officially debuted on March 4, 2019, with their debut mini album "The Dream Chapter: STAR".
